PADMA THRIVELEADS INTEGRATION

this plugin forwards your thriveleads forms to PADMA CRM.

IGNORING A FORM:

setting 'padma_ignore_this_form' will avoid form being forwarded.

You may add this to your form:

<input type="hidden" name="padma_ignore_this_form" value="1" />

COMMUNICATION USERNAME

In plugin options you can set default username for communications.
You can set it in a per form basis adding a 'padma_username' hidden field.

<input type="hidden" name="padma_username" value="nome.deusuario" />